<div id="review_2412939140" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2412939140" />
    <a title="Ana" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/5237420-ana"><img alt="Ana" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1640777235p2/5237420.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2412939140?book_show_action=true">Jun 06, 2018</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Ana" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Ana" href="/user/show/5237420-ana">Ana</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780141047973" href="/book/show/10733801-23-things-they-don-t-tell-you-about-capitalism">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5237420-ana?shelf=borrowed">borrowed</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5237420-ana?shelf=law-abiding-citizen">law-abiding-citizen</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5237420-ana?shelf=somehow-societal">somehow-societal</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5237420-ana?shelf=page-turner">page-turner</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5237420-ana?shelf=me-likey-a-lot">me-likey-a-lot</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5237420-ana?shelf=economy">economy</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5237420-ana?shelf=a-little-historical">a-little-historical</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5237420-ana?shelf=science">science</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5237420-ana?shelf=non-fiction">non-fiction</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2412939140" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14946101501756339852">An incredibly useful read for those who want to challenge their own beliefs, no matter how strongly they adhere to them. Chang is not against capitalism - far from it, actually. He believes, using the words of Churchill, that capitalism is the worst economic system - except for all others. Chang is specifically against free-market capitalism, which has done so much damage to the world economy. The writing is clear, concise and funny at times, managing to treat a difficult topic using the vocabul</span>
  <span id="freeText14946101501756339852" style="display:none">An incredibly useful read for those who want to challenge their own beliefs, no matter how strongly they adhere to them. Chang is not against capitalism - far from it, actually. He believes, using the words of Churchill, that capitalism is the worst economic system - except for all others. Chang is specifically against free-market capitalism, which has done so much damage to the world economy. The writing is clear, concise and funny at times, managing to treat a difficult topic using the vocabulary we all share. I would totally recommend it to any curious reader.</span>
  <a data-text-id="14946101501756339852" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


