              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15899233198186872394">Plain talk about capitalism - from a Cambridge economist who believes in it, but not in the free market ideology which has surrounded it for the last thirty years. Required reading for anyone who wants a grip on what&apos;s actually going on with the global economy, and anyone who likes to kid themselves they vote rationally...</span>
  <span id="freeText15899233198186872394" style="display:none">Plain talk about capitalism - from a Cambridge economist who believes in it, but not in the free market ideology which has surrounded it for the last thirty years. Required reading for anyone who wants a grip on what's actually going on with the global economy, and anyone who likes to kid themselves they vote rationally...</span>
