<div id="review_3809573641" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3809573641" />
    <a title="Claire" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/108057743-claire"><img alt="Claire" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1605898585p2/108057743.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3809573641?book_show_action=true">Feb 13, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Claire" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Claire" href="/user/show/108057743-claire">Claire</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780141047973" href="/book/show/10733801-23-things-they-don-t-tell-you-about-capitalism">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3809573641" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14276415744089810301">Ha-Joon Chang has achieved what I previously thought impossible - stripping down economics and economic theory to its bare essentials. Chang expertly myth-busts, making what could be an excruciating experience for a reader like myself, into a mind expanding and captivating read. Not only did I find the book very smart and insightful, it has genuinely contributed to shaping my world view on several topics. Plus, it was fun! Well done Ha-Joon Chang!</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

