<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/18579571-seventeen-contradictions-and-the-end-of-capitalism"><img alt="Seventeen Contradictions and the End of Capitalism" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1384017105l/18579571._SX98_.jpg" />
